metadata.name: Silhouettes
metadata.description:
Walking the streets is where I find stories to tell, which will lead each of us to thousands of different stories. I do not compose photography, photography composes me.

Camera: Nikon Z6  
Location: Sassari, Italy.


Artist: Guille Bianchi
